@startuml View Pets Flow

start

:User navigates to pets page;

:System retrieves pets from database (visible to users, not unclaimed/unadopted);

:Display list of pets with filters (species, status, etc.);

:User applies filters or searches;

:System queries database with filters;

:Display filtered results;

:User selects a pet to view details;

:System retrieves pet details and related data;

:Display pet show page;

stop

@enduml
